1. *Sluša* se kako se deca smeju u dvorištu. (He/She listens to children laughing in the yard.) 
2. On *sluša* glasove izdaleka. (He listens to voices from afar.)
3. Ona je *slušala* profesora sa pažnjom. (She was listening to the professor attentively.)
4. On *sluša* po šumu. (He listens through the forest.) 
5. *Slušaju* se pesme iz cele zemlje. (Songs from all over the country are heard.)